    "second_level": "Workflow Conventions"
  },
  {
    "id": "R60_5",
    "content": "When asked to explore a website:\n1. **Navigate** to the specified URL using browser tools\n2. **Explore** 1-2 key functionalities thoroughly\n3. **Document** observed behavior, selectors, and user flows\n4. **Implement** test based on actual exploration findings\n5. **Close** browser when exploration complete",
    "project": "nzyoni_super-todo",
    "file": "e2e-best-practices.mdc",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
    "second_level": "Workflow Conventions"
  },
  {
    "id": "R60_6",
    "content": "WAIT FOR MANUAL LOGIN: When encountering login pages during exploration, pause and wait for the user to manually enter credentials",
    "project": "nzyoni_super-todo",
    "file": "e2e-best-practices.mdc",
    "first_level": "AI Collaboration Specifications",
    "second_level": "AI Behavior & Decision Strategies"
  },
  {
