  {
    "id": "R60_10",
    "content": "1. **Spec Files**\n- **EXTREMELY SHORT** - Only high-level actions and assertions\n- Use page fixtures and component fixtures\n- No direct locators - delegate to page objects and components\n- Only contain assertions (`expect()`) and high-level method calls\n- Example: `await sideNavigation.userMenu.switchOrganization()`",
    "project": "nzyoni_super-todo",
    "file": "e2e-best-practices.mdc",
    "first_level": "Architecture & Design",
    "second_level": "System Architecture"
  },
  {
    "id": "R60_11",
    "content": "2. **E2E Page Objects** (`pages/*.page.ts`)\n- Represent actual web application pages\n- Contain page-specific actions and workflows\n- Include e2e-components as needed\n- Handle loading states and page-specific logic\n- Expose user actions for that particular page",
    "project": "nzyoni_super-todo",
    "file": "e2e-best-practices.mdc",
    "first_level": "Architecture & Design",
    "second_level": "System Architecture"
  },
  {
    "id": "R60_12",
    "content": "3. **E2E Components** (`components/*.ts`)\n- Represent reusable UI components from `src/components`\n- One file per component type\n- Reusable across multiple pages\n- Contain component-specific locators and actions\n- **Include high-level methods** that handle complex workflows internally",
    "project": "nzyoni_super-todo",
    "file": "e2e-best-practices.mdc",
    "first_level": "Architecture & Design",
    "second_level": "System Architecture"
  },
